message.body: Hey! Just thinking about you. Hope you are doing well. We should catch up one if these days. Preferably when it is above freezing.

I have thought about catching up with you so many times in the last month. We have a HUGE launch at work next week and then things should be slightly less crazy for me. Maybe we can have dinner or drinks at the end of the month?
That sounds great! No worries. Just let me know when you have some free time. I hope everything goes well with ur launch.
